1
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:29,660
♪In the stormy night♪

2
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:37,340
♪The dark hair of a charming woman
is reflected in the flame of a candle♪

3
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:41,300
♪Shrouded by year
after year of memories♪

4
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:45,780
♪I can do nothing
but feign indifference♪

5
00:00:46,220 --> 00:00:53,140
♪Outlining your cheeks♪

6
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:55,540
♪Together and apart,
just like quicksand♪

7
00:00:55,740 --> 00:00:57,420
♪I'm meant to make peace with myself♪

8
00:00:57,660 --> 00:01:01,140
♪Rebuild or crumble♪

9
00:01:01,420 --> 00:01:03,780
♪Drift away in the clouds♪

10
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:05,660
♪Driving away♪

11
00:01:06,020 --> 00:01:09,300
♪Your dashing pretense♪

12
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:11,620
♪A drunken dream♪

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:13,500
♪A person I miss♪

14
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:16,860
♪Of course I know if it's real♪

15
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:21,660
♪Even if you're just by my side♪

16
00:01:22,180 --> 00:01:28,220
♪I want to hold on to you
but I can only play dumb♪

17
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:35,060
[In Blossom]

18
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:38,820
[Episode 27]

19
00:02:09,270 --> 00:02:10,440
What is your name?

20
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,030
Zhi.

21
00:02:14,750 --> 00:02:16,520
You know Dancing Among the Clouds?

22
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:19,670
I have been practicing with Miss Yun,

23
00:02:19,670 --> 00:02:20,910
so I know it.

24
00:02:32,750 --> 00:02:35,060
Okay, you are selected.

25
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:59,000
Take the girls away.

26
00:03:35,460 --> 00:03:37,380
[Luoyi]

27
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:52,670
Have we arrived so soon?

28
00:03:59,550 --> 00:04:00,750
It was left behind by Miss Shangguan.

29
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:02,550
They went this way.

30
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:18,550
No personal belongings
are allowed in Shiluo Garden.

31
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:20,070
Girls,

32
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:22,270
your purses,

33
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,510
sachets, handkerchiefs

34
00:04:24,670 --> 00:04:26,760
- must be removed
- So that place is Shiluo Garden.

35
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,720
- and left here.
- This should be the place.

36
00:04:48,270 --> 00:04:49,000
I'm so sorry.

37
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:11,550
Sir, there is no trace
of fragrant powder ahead there.

38
00:05:12,070 --> 00:05:13,110
I don't find any on my side either.

39
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,270
That's strange.

40
00:05:18,550 --> 00:05:19,790
Is there something wrong, sir?

41
00:05:20,350 --> 00:05:21,600
This house is small.

42
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:24,160
It doesn't look like a place
used to entertain dignitaries.

43
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:25,920
Moreover,

44
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:28,440
they have always acted
mysteriously and inconspicuously.

45
00:05:29,110 --> 00:05:31,350
This house is close
to the downtown area.

46
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,000
The sound of musical instruments

47
00:05:33,110 --> 00:05:35,350
would be easily heard by passers-by.

48
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:37,720
Ze,

49
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:39,510
go and see
if this house has a back door.

50
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,320
Miss Yun, ask around

51
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:43,000
about this house.

52
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:43,720
Okay.

53
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:44,510
Yes, sir.

54
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,730
Fill it.

55
00:05:53,670 --> 00:05:54,440
Beauty.

56
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:56,790
Have a drink with me.

57
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:59,490
Drink up, sir.

58
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,720
Come on.

59
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:03,830
Shiluo Garden.

60
00:06:04,530 --> 00:06:06,790
Sir, my clothes are new.

61
00:06:06,790 --> 00:06:08,110
This should be it.

62
00:06:11,290 --> 00:06:13,490
Keep drinking, keep pouring.

63
00:06:13,490 --> 00:06:14,540
Pour it for me.

64
00:06:14,540 --> 00:06:15,250
Come on.

65
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:18,010
Come on, beauty.

66
00:06:18,330 --> 00:06:18,890
Drink.

67
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:42,160
Girls,

68
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,760
starting today,

69
00:06:44,110 --> 00:06:46,110
you are part of Shiluo Garden.

70
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:50,720
This Shiluo Garden
is not a usual place of entertainment.

71
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:54,480
As long as all of you are obedient,

72
00:06:55,070 --> 00:06:56,070
in the future,

73
00:06:56,510 --> 00:06:59,350
you will enjoy endless glory and wealth.

74
00:07:09,350 --> 00:07:10,440
That's a lot.

75
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:11,880
Look.

76
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,270
How nice.

77
00:07:16,390 --> 00:07:19,510
Shower and get changed.
After that, wait to be summoned.

78
00:07:20,350 --> 00:07:21,350
Yes, madam.

79
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,550
Hurry up.

80
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:26,390
How lovely.

81
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,200
Indeed.

82
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:45,720
Mr. Pan, this house has no back door.

83
00:07:46,410 --> 00:07:47,940
Sir,
I just asked the neighbor next door.

84
00:07:47,940 --> 00:07:49,280
They said no one lives here.

85
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:51,170
- How about at night?
- I asked several families.

86
00:07:51,170 --> 00:07:52,920
They all say this is an abandoned house.

87
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,280
No one has lived here for a long time.

88
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:57,350
This is bad.

89
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,790
There must be a secret passage here.

90
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,350
Search.

91
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:12,760
- Yes.
- Okay.

92
00:08:36,350 --> 00:08:37,080
Found it!

93
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:42,550
Well, look! I've never

94
00:08:42,670 --> 00:08:44,470
worn such beautiful clothes in my life!

95
00:08:44,550 --> 00:08:46,440
Yeah, look at this hairpin ring.

96
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:48,710
I bit it just now. It really is gold!

97
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:51,200
Just as the legends say, Shiluo Garden

98
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:52,280
is full of gold and jewels.

99
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,790
We will surely have a good life
in the future.

100
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:54,790
Yes.

101
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:57,030
When Yunchang first came here,

102
00:08:57,590 --> 00:09:00,840
she must have thought that she would be
wearing gold and jade in the future,

103
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:02,350
leading a life of wealth and honor.

104
00:09:03,670 --> 00:09:06,150
Little did she know
that this magnificent Shiluo Garden

105
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:09,520
is actually a devil's cave
that devours people whole.

106
00:09:24,910 --> 00:09:26,000
Stop there.

107
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,180
Madam Wan.

108
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:31,470
What are you doing here?

109
00:09:32,670 --> 00:09:34,910
I... I want to relieve myself.

110
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:39,520
Shiluo Garden has its rules.

111
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,590
See what you should,

112
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:44,790
and don't see what you shouldn't.

113
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:51,760
Otherwise, you will be like her.

114
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,110
Not only deaf,

115
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:56,030
but also mute.

116
00:09:57,520 --> 00:10:00,110
She looks pathetic now, right?

117
00:10:00,710 --> 00:10:01,880
Ten years ago,

118
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:06,150
she was also the most popular girl
in Shiluo Garden.

119
00:10:07,230 --> 00:10:09,550
Because she slapped the lead dancer,

120
00:10:09,590 --> 00:10:11,350
she was punished by Mr. Zuo.

121
00:10:11,470 --> 00:10:12,280
Finally,

122
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:15,110
she ended up like this.

123
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,710
Take a look at this sachet.

124
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,260
Embroidered sachet.

125
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:31,880
Come and take a look.

126
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,790
Come and take a look.

127
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:37,080
- Come and take a look at this sachet.
- Take a look at this paper umbrella.

128
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,170
Embroidered sachet.

129
00:10:40,290 --> 00:10:43,760
Sachet, embroidered sachet.

130
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:49,670
Greetings, sir.

131
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:55,960
Fill it already.

132
00:10:56,050 --> 00:10:58,000
- Come on, sir. Let's drink.
- Come on.

133
00:10:58,470 --> 00:10:59,280
I'll fill it for you.

134
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:05,760
Here.

135
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:07,280
Come on.

136
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,760
Beauty, come and have a drink.

137
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:17,880
Come on, drink.

138
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,790
This place is securely guarded.

139
00:11:29,470 --> 00:11:31,520
Looks like there is no way
to send a message to Pan Yue.

140
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:34,440
I hope he can see the clues
I left behind

141
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:36,280
and find this place as soon as possible.

142
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,710
The guests in this room

143
00:11:47,030 --> 00:11:49,440
are the most exalted
among our distinguished guests.

144
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,350
Perform well.

145
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,840
If something goes wrong,

146
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:58,230
even I can't protect you girls.

147
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:00,550
Yes, madam.

148
00:12:14,470 --> 00:12:16,320
Mr. Zuo, Mr. He,

149
00:12:17,110 --> 00:12:19,520
the girls are ready.

150
00:12:22,350 --> 00:12:24,230
So he is the owner of Shiluo Garden.

151
00:12:24,910 --> 00:12:27,110
Could he be the mastermind
behind the Ripple Organization?

152
00:12:27,670 --> 00:12:28,470
Mr. Zuo,

153
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:30,640
we'll talk about those matters later.

154
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:33,030
Let's enjoy the dance now.

155
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:33,760
Sure.

156
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,550
Let's get started, girls.

157
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:39,760
Yes.

158
00:13:53,030 --> 00:13:55,200
Good.

159
00:14:00,470 --> 00:14:03,470
I heard that this dance
is Shiluo Garden's unique skill.

160
00:14:04,030 --> 00:14:06,840
Sure enough, seeing it once is better
than hearing it a hundred times.

161
00:14:08,520 --> 00:14:10,440
Thank you, Mr. Zuo.

162
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:11,710
Mr. He,

163
00:14:12,670 --> 00:14:14,670
Shiluo Garden's sincerity to you

164
00:14:15,470 --> 00:14:17,230
is not merely this dance.

165
00:14:27,710 --> 00:14:29,320
You are asking me for a favor.

166
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:30,880
But until now,

167
00:14:31,030 --> 00:14:33,760
I haven't even met your master
in person.

168
00:14:34,230 --> 00:14:35,960
I don't know

169
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,150
who he is.

170
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:40,200
If an accident happens…

171
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,280
Don't worry, Mr. He.

172
00:14:41,590 --> 00:14:43,080
The reason our master never showed up

173
00:14:43,230 --> 00:14:45,710
is all for your safety.

174
00:14:46,230 --> 00:14:48,760
If something happens in the future,

175
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:50,910
the investigations won't
find their way to you, Mr. He.

176
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:53,280
It seems like Mr. Zuo

177
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,520
is just the steward of Shiluo Garden.

178
00:14:56,150 --> 00:14:57,550
There is another mastermind behind him.

179
00:14:58,470 --> 00:15:01,590
Since you have said so, Mr. Zuo,

180
00:15:02,280 --> 00:15:03,470
if I am to refuse again,

181
00:15:03,790 --> 00:15:06,000
I might come off as disagreeable.

182
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,520
The thing you requested is here.

183
00:15:21,550 --> 00:15:22,550
Thank you, Mr. He.

184
00:15:25,880 --> 00:15:28,320
Madam Wan, serve Mr. He well.

185
00:15:28,590 --> 00:15:30,230
Make sure Mr. He is satisfied.

186
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:32,030
Rest assured, Mr. Zuo.

187
00:15:44,910 --> 00:15:46,880
It seems that the real purpose
of Shiluo Garden

188
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:49,790
is to collude with imperial officials

189
00:15:50,230 --> 00:15:52,000
and do some shady businesses.

190
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:56,000
What exactly did Mr. He give to Mr. Zuo?

191
00:15:56,350 --> 00:15:57,110
Zhi.

192
00:15:58,400 --> 00:15:59,110
Madam.

193
00:15:59,280 --> 00:16:02,440
Mr. He wanted you to serve him alone.

194
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:04,590
Hurry up and go in.

195
00:16:15,760 --> 00:16:16,670
Come on.

196
00:16:20,150 --> 00:16:22,590
A hat with seven pearl beads
inlaid on the top.

197
00:16:22,590 --> 00:16:25,230
What? Do you want the guards
to search the streets now?

198
00:16:25,880 --> 00:16:26,440
That's right.

199
00:16:27,910 --> 00:16:30,030
If you search the streets now,
you will definitely alert the enemy.

200
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:31,910
The later we find her,

201
00:16:32,350 --> 00:16:33,590
the more danger she would be in.

202
00:16:36,880 --> 00:16:39,320
Okay, if your mind is set,

203
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:40,440
then do it.

204
00:16:42,030 --> 00:16:42,920
Thank you, Your Highness.

205
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:46,490
Three pairs of pearl earrings,
a total of 12 beads.

206
00:16:46,910 --> 00:16:48,280
A pair of gold bracelets.

207
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:49,960
A string of agate beads.

208
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:52,320
Two strings of amber beads.

209
00:16:52,910 --> 00:16:53,760
Mr. Sun.

210
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:57,470
The number of pearls on the gift list
seems to be wrong.

211
00:17:01,670 --> 00:17:02,320
Who is there?

212
00:17:08,430 --> 00:17:09,110
Your Highness!

213
00:17:09,520 --> 00:17:10,520
Are you okay, Your Highness?

214
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:13,430
I'm fine. Quickly, lead your men
to chase the assassin.

215
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:15,400
Mr. Sun, take care of Her Highness.

216
00:17:15,680 --> 00:17:16,950
I will lead the imperial guards
to capture the assassin.

217
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:18,680
Yes.

218
00:17:21,230 --> 00:17:24,920
Beauty, that dance you did just now

219
00:17:25,110 --> 00:17:28,590
really took away my soul.

220
00:17:29,710 --> 00:17:32,310
Sir, please have something to eat.

221
00:17:35,590 --> 00:17:36,470
Mr. He.

222
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:38,430
The night is still young.

223
00:17:38,710 --> 00:17:40,230
Why should you rush?

224
00:17:40,590 --> 00:17:42,920
Why don't I play a drinking game
with you?

225
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:45,560
What kind of drinking game
do you want to play?

226
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:50,800
Why don't we play
guessing the hidden coin?

227
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:52,990
Sure.

228
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:59,310
Guess, which one?

229
00:18:07,950 --> 00:18:10,440
Beauty, you guessed it right.

230
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:12,990
Mr. He, please drink.

231
00:18:15,710 --> 00:18:18,190
It's your turn to drink this time.

232
00:18:20,280 --> 00:18:21,400
Guess again.

233
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:28,640
Left side.

234
00:18:30,190 --> 00:18:31,640
Impressive, beauty.

235
00:18:32,230 --> 00:18:34,800
I'm just lucky. Drink up, Mr. He.

236
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:38,640
It's obvious
that whenever you are about to win,

237
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:40,760
you will slightly raise your eyebrow.

238
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:45,040
Come on, let's continue.

239
00:18:45,830 --> 00:18:47,880
Mr. He, let me warm you
a few more pots of good wine.

240
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:02,680
How can I get in?

241
00:19:12,520 --> 00:19:14,280
Go and warm some pots of good wine
for Mr. He.

242
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:16,310
Also,

243
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,830
Mr. He said he wanted something
to spice things up.

244
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:22,280
Yes.

245
00:19:29,110 --> 00:19:30,520
Search every house!

246
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:31,440
Yes, sir!

247
00:20:09,520 --> 00:20:11,350
Sir, let's continue.

248
00:20:12,280 --> 00:20:17,310
Beauty, are you trying to get me drunk?

249
00:20:21,020 --> 00:20:23,290
If you are afraid of losing
and don't want to play, just say so.

250
00:20:23,290 --> 00:20:24,460
Why bother acting like a sore loser?

251
00:20:31,070 --> 00:20:33,710
So what if I lose to a beauty?

252
00:20:35,310 --> 00:20:36,560
Then let's have one game
to determine the outcome.

253
00:20:36,760 --> 00:20:39,040
The loser has to down this pot.

254
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:46,300
Mr. He.

255
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:49,880
I want to ride a horse!

256
00:20:49,880 --> 00:20:51,190
Sir! Are you okay, sir?

257
00:20:51,300 --> 00:20:52,200
Go away!

258
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:53,480
Help!

259
00:20:53,480 --> 00:20:54,920
- Sir!
- Somebody, help!

260
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:56,460
- Come quickly.
- Hurry, something happened to Mr. He.

261
00:20:57,190 --> 00:20:59,280
- Hurry up, he is an important guest!
- Sir!

262
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:01,080
If something goes wrong with him,

263
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:02,640
we can't afford it!

264
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:04,440
Be careful, Mr. He.

265
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:06,520
Mr. He!

266
00:21:38,310 --> 00:21:39,830
It turns out that the pattern
painted on the token

267
00:21:40,520 --> 00:21:42,310
is not a water ripple at all.

268
00:21:43,280 --> 00:21:45,560
It's just a part
of this ram horn totem.

269
00:21:45,710 --> 00:21:51,310
Water... Water ripples are...

270
00:21:51,950 --> 00:21:55,310
Yang...

271
00:21:56,380 --> 00:21:57,130
Yang.

272
00:21:58,190 --> 00:22:01,400
So, the "Yang" mentioned by Gu Yong
before he died

273
00:22:01,710 --> 00:22:03,070
is not the surname Yang,

274
00:22:03,710 --> 00:22:05,190
but referring to the rams.

