00:22:07,900 --> 00:22:14,020
[Custom Clearance Document]

276
00:22:20,580 --> 00:22:22,380
[Salt Distribution Commandant,
He Hongyi, to govern the prisons.]

277
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,710
Customs clearance document?

278
00:22:25,040 --> 00:22:26,640
Salt Distribution Commandant?

279
00:22:28,110 --> 00:22:29,280
Could this be related to the salt

280
00:22:29,280 --> 00:22:31,190
in the back mountains
of Xinzheng Academy?

281
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:08,230
Yang Caiwei, please be safe.

282
00:23:09,270 --> 00:23:10,630
It is such
a huge underground pleasure house.

283
00:23:11,320 --> 00:23:13,520
If it is really hidden
among the streets,

284
00:23:13,880 --> 00:23:15,400
