285
00:23:17,110 --> 00:23:18,400
I can definitely find it.

286
00:23:18,560 --> 00:23:19,760
I can find it for sure.

287
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:21,040
Keep searching.

288
00:23:21,110 --> 00:23:21,800
Yes, sir.

289
00:24:19,590 --> 00:24:22,710
May my god hear my call.

290
00:24:22,950 --> 00:24:25,310
Darkness, cover me.

291
00:24:25,800 --> 00:24:27,950
Darkness, give me godly power.

292
00:24:28,520 --> 00:24:32,070
May the shadow of darkness
spread throughout the world.

293
00:24:32,520 --> 00:24:36,350
May your lives
be swallowed up by darkness.

294
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,040
Master.

295
00:24:52,560 --> 00:24:53,950
What is it?

296
00:24:55,590 --> 00:24:56,880
Mr. He went crazy after drinking.

297
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:58,640
He is awake now.

298
00:24:59,280 --> 00:24:59,990
Mr. He said

299
00:25:00,100 --> 00:25:01,310
it was a new courtesan

300
00:25:01,310 --> 00:25:02,640
who secretly put

301
00:25:02,800 --> 00:25:04,190
excessive five minerals powder
in his wine.

302
00:25:05,110 --> 00:25:06,590
I'm afraid an outsider
might have sneaked in.

303
00:25:08,110 --> 00:25:08,830
Kill her.

304
00:25:08,990 --> 00:25:09,590
Yes.

305
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:23,350
I have to find a way to escape quickly.

306
00:25:24,440 --> 00:25:25,590
You, go over there.

307
00:25:25,800 --> 00:25:27,110
Even if you have to turn
the place upside down,

308
00:25:27,110 --> 00:25:28,280
find her.

309
00:25:28,350 --> 00:25:28,950
Yes, sir!

310
00:25:29,760 --> 00:25:30,680
What's going on?

311
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:32,680
I'm sorry, sir.

312
00:25:32,920 --> 00:25:34,920
There's a thief in Shiluo Garden today.

313
00:25:35,110 --> 00:25:35,800
Hurry up.

314
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:36,640
How disappointing.

315
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:38,920
- Sir, please don't be angry.
- We'll send you back.

316
00:25:39,180 --> 00:25:40,770
You go and search over there.
I'll take this side.

317
00:25:40,990 --> 00:25:42,070
We must find her!

318
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:42,830
Yes!

319
00:26:12,350 --> 00:26:13,040
Hold on.

320
00:26:17,070 --> 00:26:18,990
So much swill. Is this all yours?

321
00:26:19,800 --> 00:26:20,400
Yes.

322
00:26:25,340 --> 00:26:27,060
