323
00:26:27,830 --> 00:26:29,040
Everyone, search.

324
00:26:29,310 --> 00:26:29,880
Let's go.

325
00:26:40,280 --> 00:26:40,830
Search every corner.

326
00:26:42,110 --> 00:26:42,830
Any clues over there?

327
00:26:42,990 --> 00:26:43,520
No.

328
00:26:43,590 --> 00:26:45,110
