- Yes, sir.

329
00:26:45,590 --> 00:26:46,590
Nothing here either.

330
00:26:48,120 --> 00:26:49,560
Nothing. Go there and have a look.

331
00:26:49,590 --> 00:26:50,040
Quiet.

332
00:26:50,310 --> 00:26:50,760
