341
00:27:13,530 --> 00:27:14,570
Be careful.

342
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:16,490
I'll help you.

343
00:27:17,560 --> 00:27:19,190
Madam Wan, we couldn't find her
in the backyard.

344
00:27:19,800 --> 00:27:21,070
Where did she go?

345
00:27:22,800 --> 00:27:23,920
Madam Wan, bad news.

346
00:27:23,990 --> 00:27:25,110
Some imperial guards broke in.

347
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:27,160
What? Imperial guards?

348
00:27:40,640 --> 00:27:42,800
What are you doing?
This is a private residence.

349
00:27:42,990 --> 00:27:45,110
Even imperial guards have no right
to break in here.

350
00:27:45,470 --> 00:27:48,280
An assassination attempt on Her Highness.
We are searching for the culprit.

351
00:27:48,950 --> 00:27:51,280
What does that have to do with us?

352
00:27:51,760 --> 00:27:53,190
The owner of this house

353
00:27:53,520 --> 00:27:56,040
is not someone you can afford to offend.

354
00:27:58,760 --> 00:28:01,400
Where is that girl named Zhi?

355
00:28:06,350 --> 00:28:07,190
I have no idea.

356
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:08,830
I'm looking for her too.

357
00:28:13,350 --> 00:28:13,920
Search the place.

358
00:28:13,950 --> 00:28:14,590
Follow me.

359
00:28:46,990 --> 00:28:48,160
Over here, catch him.

360
00:28:49,190 --> 00:28:49,880
Young Master.

361
00:28:51,080 --> 00:28:51,540
Young Master.

362
00:28:52,310 --> 00:28:53,760
How is it? Did you find her?

363
00:28:54,520 --> 00:28:56,110
I've searched the place.
I couldn't find her.

364
00:28:56,880 --> 00:28:58,520
But a carriage just left
from the back door.

365
00:28:59,110 --> 00:28:59,710
However,

366
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,990
the carriage belongs to us,
the Pan Family.

367
00:29:05,900 --> 00:29:09,260
[Pan Mansion]

368
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:20,950
Where is she?

369
00:29:24,990 --> 00:29:26,040
How dare you?

370
00:29:26,520 --> 00:29:28,470
Hand over Shangguan Zhi.

371
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:30,590
Otherwise, don't blame me
for ignoring our blood ties.

372
00:29:33,110 --> 00:29:34,590
Shangguan Zhi.

373
00:29:36,590 --> 00:29:38,350
Think it over before you speak.

374
00:29:45,040 --> 00:29:46,590
Do you want Shangguan Zhi

375
00:29:48,350 --> 00:29:50,190
or Yang Ji'an's daughter,

376
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:51,640
Yang Caiwei?

377
00:29:56,760 --> 00:29:57,520
How did you know?

378
00:29:59,040 --> 00:30:01,680
Put down your sword
before talking to your father.

379
00:30:21,760 --> 00:30:23,230
That day, I went to see you

380
00:30:23,990 --> 00:30:26,110
to talk about the marriage.

381
00:30:27,470 --> 00:30:28,800
However, I saw

382
00:30:31,280 --> 00:30:32,990
you with her.

383
00:30:35,860 --> 00:30:36,420
Caiwei.

384
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:38,830
It's good to have you here.

385
00:30:41,310 --> 00:30:43,920
You kept calling her Caiwei

386
00:30:44,920 --> 00:30:47,310
and talking about your childhood.

387
00:30:48,830 --> 00:30:50,760
Recalling all the various incidents,

388
00:30:53,110 --> 00:30:55,470
you never liked Shangguan Zhi.

389
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:58,280
How could you suddenly
fall in love with her?

390
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:01,830
Although I don't know what happened,

391
00:31:02,110 --> 00:31:03,160
I guess

392
00:31:04,110 --> 00:31:05,590
Yang Caiwei didn't die.

393
00:31:05,990 --> 00:31:07,700
She's disguised
as Shangguan Zhi instead.

394
00:31:09,180 --> 00:31:10,160
Moreover,

395
00:31:10,710 --> 00:31:13,630
