Yang Ji'an's old case with you.

396
00:31:15,070 --> 00:31:17,040
Am I right?

397
00:31:22,030 --> 00:31:23,990
Yang Ji'an's family
was murdered back then.

398
00:31:24,890 --> 00:31:27,150
As his friend,
you watched from the sidelines

399
00:31:27,150 --> 00:31:28,110
without doing anything about it.

400
00:31:28,750 --> 00:31:30,030
To this day,

401
00:31:30,320 --> 00:31:31,720
do you still want
to be their accomplice?

402
00:31:31,870 --> 00:31:33,680
Not sparing even Yang Ji'an's daughter?

403
00:31:33,920 --> 00:31:35,960
Am I so despicable in your eyes?

404
00:31:37,110 --> 00:31:38,560
If I were an accomplice,

405
00:31:40,850 --> 00:31:44,110
Yang Caiwei would have died
a hundred times.

406
00:31:44,800 --> 00:31:46,560
Then, why did you show up
at the Shiluo Garden?

407
00:31:46,870 --> 00:31:48,110
I was invited there by my colleagues.

408
00:31:48,630 --> 00:31:50,320
I have no intention
of joining any party,

409
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:53,750
but I have to do things accordingly.

410
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,720
I took Yang Caiwei away

411
00:31:58,630 --> 00:32:00,800
because I was afraid
that this would implicate the Pan family.

412
00:32:02,870 --> 00:32:04,630
I can return her to you now,

413
00:32:05,870 --> 00:32:06,440
but

414
00:32:07,270 --> 00:32:10,200
