415
00:32:11,560 --> 00:32:13,630
You and Her Highness
are getting married soon.

416
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:15,200
Why do you still want to be with her?

417
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:18,150
This matter has progressed this far.

418
00:32:18,390 --> 00:32:20,320
You're setting yourself on fire,
did you know that?

419
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:22,110
Do you want to end up like Yang Ji'an?

420
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:25,320
I only live once.

421
00:32:26,230 --> 00:32:27,270
So what if I die?

422
00:32:27,510 --> 00:32:29,150
You are deceiving the Emperor!

423
00:32:29,150 --> 00:32:29,960
I know.

424
00:32:30,560 --> 00:32:31,840
That's why, a few months ago,

425
00:32:32,560 --> 00:32:33,720
I promised you

426
00:32:34,510 --> 00:32:35,800
to sever my ties with the Pan family.

427
00:32:36,840 --> 00:32:38,320
So what if you could find her?

428
00:32:38,390 --> 00:32:39,870
That's my own business.

429
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:41,630
I won't bother you anymore.

430
00:32:41,750 --> 00:32:42,320
Fine.

431
00:32:43,750 --> 00:32:45,840
I'll tell you where she is,

432
00:32:46,230 --> 00:32:47,960
but starting from today,

433
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:49,870
your ties with the Pan family

434
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:52,960
will be severed.

435
00:32:53,480 --> 00:32:54,800
It's a deal.

436
00:32:55,680 --> 00:32:57,110
Sever your ties?

437
00:33:00,600 --> 00:33:01,440
Fine.

438
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:04,200
It's my fault.

439
00:33:06,270 --> 00:33:08,870
I tried to become associated
with the imperial families

440
00:33:09,870 --> 00:33:11,680
but ended up
getting into this muddy water.

441
00:33:11,720 --> 00:33:13,320
But I don't understand.

442
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:18,680
Why is Her Highness willing
to destroy her reputation

443
00:33:19,960 --> 00:33:22,080
to act in this show with you?

444
00:33:25,270 --> 00:33:27,320
Not everyone is like you, Father.

445
00:33:28,080 --> 00:33:29,750
You only care about yourself.

446
00:33:31,560 --> 00:33:32,230
Men,

447
00:33:33,840 --> 00:33:34,510
bring her out.

448
00:33:38,630 --> 00:33:39,350
Caiwei.

449
00:33:40,600 --> 00:33:42,390
How are you? Are you okay?

450
00:33:43,230 --> 00:33:43,920
I'm okay.

451
00:33:45,080 --> 00:33:45,680
Leave.

452
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:47,870
Remember.

453
00:33:48,840 --> 00:33:51,800
I've never seen you two tonight.

454
00:33:54,350 --> 00:33:55,030
Let's go.

455
00:34:25,720 --> 00:34:26,940
Anyway,

456
00:34:27,600 --> 00:34:29,660
