for helping me this time.

457
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:32,830
I know.

458
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:34,520
I'm very grateful to him.

459
00:34:35,870 --> 00:34:36,920
But it seems like I can never

460
00:34:40,000 --> 00:34:42,480
