465
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:08,110
I entered a secluded room
in Shiluo Garden.

466
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:09,550
There was a tapestry inside.

467
00:35:09,620 --> 00:35:11,650
The pattern on it
was exactly the same as the ripples.

468
00:35:11,820 --> 00:35:13,140
