505
00:36:48,070 --> 00:36:50,520
Master, what should we do now?

506
00:36:52,350 --> 00:36:53,550
Send someone to investigate

507
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:56,830
and find out if Pan Jin
is involved in this matter.

508
00:36:57,630 --> 00:36:58,150
Yes.

509
00:36:58,550 --> 00:37:00,480
By the way,
the traitor has been eliminated.

510
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:05,630
